286
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:55,570
estando

287
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:55,570
nu,

288
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:55,570
enfrenta

289
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:55,570
as

290
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:55,570
inúmeras

291
00:15:51,780 --> 00:15:55,570
ondas

